    "description": "<strong>Game only available in French</strong><br><br>Dive into a case full of secrets... In this point'n'click game, you will have to find clues in the scenery, question the suspects, and get to the truth by avoiding false leads. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/1bb113528fca2f4a5b97b94461675f4c.poster.avif?t=1681985238\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/1bb113528fca2f4a5b97b94461675f4c.webm?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/1bb113528fca2f4a5b97b94461675f4c.mp4?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make connections between clues and solve problems to set the wheels of the case in motion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/fd0e6f190dc95dd1dd93fa360db52698.poster.avif?t=1681985238\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/fd0e6f190dc95dd1dd93fa360db52698.webm?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/fd0e6f190dc95dd1dd93fa360db52698.mp4?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as <strong>different actors</strong> of a criminal procedure and discover the stages of a case from different angles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/61fc4742094810a2f63d47b48619824d.poster.avif?t=1681985238\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/61fc4742094810a2f63d47b48619824d.webm?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294590/extras/61fc4742094810a2f63d47b48619824d.mp4?t=1681985238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Where is the key to this true story, stored in the Gard departmental archives? It's up to you to find out... But beware, some people are not ready to empty their bag so easily.",
